{
  "message": "chore(deps): add animation and analytics dependencies\n\nAdd four new dependencies to support enhanced UI animations and\ncomprehensive analytics tracking:\n\nDependencies added:\n- @vercel/analytics (^1.4.1): Official Vercel Analytics React component\n  for automatic pageview tracking and custom event support. Replaces\n  manual Script injection with proper SDK integration.\n\n- @vercel/speed-insights (^1.1.0): Official Vercel Speed Insights\n  component for Core Web Vitals monitoring. Provides real-user\n  performance metrics without manual configuration.\n\n- framer-motion (^11.15.0): Production-ready animation library for\n  React. Used by motion components (motion-provider, motion/index) for\n  smooth, performant animations throughout the wizard and flywheel pages.\n\n- @use-gesture/react (^10.3.1): React hooks for gesture handling\n  (drag, pinch, scroll). Enables touch-friendly interactions for the\n  interactive flywheel visualization and future mobile-optimized UI.\n\nThese dependencies enable the server-side analytics tracking,\nofficial Vercel integration, and enhanced motion design that follow\nin subsequent commits.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
